Pathology_Details: Invasive well-differentiated squamous cell carcinoma, p16 negative
Plans: Proceed with radiotherapy, further investigation of the left thyroid lobe mass, medical oncology consultation, PEG tube insertion, dentistry evaluation, and audiology testing
